thread.title: BRIEF-Private equity firm EQT closes eighth equity fund at EUR 10.75 bln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Private equity firm EQT closes eighth equity fund at EUR 10.75 bln
text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) -
* PRIVATE EQUITY FIRM EQT SAYS CLOSES EIGHTH EQUITY FUND AT EUR 10.75 BILLION
* SAYS INVESTOR DEMAND FROM BOTH EXISTING AND NEW INVESTORS WAS STRONG WITH APPROXIMATELY 70% OF THE COMMITMENTS TO EQT VIII MADE BY INVESTORS IN THE PREDECESSOR EQUITY FUND, EQT VII
* THE FUND OFFICIALLY LAUNCHED IN SEPTEMBER 2017 * THE FUNDRAISING WAS LED BY THE IN-HOUSE INVESTOR RELATIONS TEAM WITHIN EQT PARTNERS Source text: bit.ly/2EMvE1f (Stockholm Newsroom)
